    While Cray has sold several Cray XT systems with the portals network
    API, they also provide a Cray-supported MPI implementation.<br>
    So, the question is how many Cray XT systems choose to deploy
    OpenMPI *and* will want to upgrade to OpenMPI 1.7?<br>
    <br>
    -Paul<br>
